          </summary>
          <div class="accordion-content">
            <p>One of MT5's biggest advantages over MT4 is the integrated economic calendar. This shows upcoming economic events, their expected impact, previous readings, and forecasts - all without leaving the platform.</p>
            <p>You can filter events by country, impact level (high, medium, low), and date range. Events are displayed in real-time with automatic updates as data is released.</p>
            <p>For fundamental traders, this eliminates the need for external websites like Forex Factory or Investing.com - everything you need is built into MT5.</p>
            <div class="broker-note">
              <strong>Pro Tip:</strong> Use the calendar to avoid trading during high-impact news events, or strategically trade the volatility around major releases.
            </div>
          </div>
        </details>

        <details class="accordion-item">
          <summary class="accordion-header">
            <span class="accordion-icon">üìä</span>
            <span class="accordion-title">Depth of Market (DOM)</span>
          </summary>
          <div class="accordion-content">
